body:
@Achal1607 please squash all commits into one and force push into your branch once the PR is ready - since we don't use the gh squash function.

I did also add a few labels so that the LSP and VSCode extension tests run when this PR syncs the next time.

Since PRs are directly linked from the release notes I am going to edit and remove the instructions from the PR template text to clean it up a bit. Feel free to simply remove the text yourself in future PRs.
